install dependencies:
     $ cd src && npm install

   run the app:
     $ DEBUG=src:* npm start

     run mocha test case one by one
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestCalendarController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestCalendarController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestConnectionController_mocha.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestFolderController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestLifeEventController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestNewsController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestNoteController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestNotificationController.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestPostController_mocha.js
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestSkillController.js   - (all hard coded. so not functioning)
     $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/TestUserController.js   - (some hard coded user_id. so those functions are not functioning)

   Note:-
   #1. The below functions in the UserController functions are hard code with user_id and some other values. so these functions are not added in test case.
        (addEducationDetail,deleteEducationDetail)(saveSkillInfo,getSkills)(connectionCount)(getNewsCategories,deleteNewsCategory,addNewsChannel,getNewsChannels,deleteNewsChannel)(getSavedArticles,deleteSavedArticle)(file upload and passing as json object having issue)

   #2. Email and Sms notifications are not working, so forget password and reset password functions testcases are failing.

   #3. Can run all the test case at once using, $ ./node_module/.bin/mocha ./test/*
       But it may fail because of some other old test controller files are there. once if we remove those controllers, we can run all at once.
       (TestConnectionController.js,TestCommentController.js,TestPostController.js,TestSessionController.js,bundle.js,vendors.js)



   # gulp development task
   gulp scripts

   # gulp production task
   gulp deploy

   # webpack dev
   npm dev run

   # webpack dev server
   webpack-dev-server